PayOnDelivery,is,an,online,payment,platform,for,buying,and,selling,items,on,online,marketplaces,such,as,Craigslist,Users,do,not,pay,for,items,until,they,are,delivered,The,PayOnDelivery,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,PayOnDelivery,with,other,applications,Public,documentation,is,not,available,interested,developers,should,sign,up,here,for,API,access,http,payondelivery,com,apip,joinus